<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Integrity" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Integrity,</orth> freedom from any falseness and dishonesty, perfect uprightness: <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 2, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.205" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 205</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.107.205" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.356" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 356</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Alls IV, 2, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.240" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 240</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.108" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.59" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.145" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 170</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 1, 159</bibl> (or is it here a sound and untainted state in general?). <bibl n="shak. tit 1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 44</bibl>. With <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>my i. to heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.454" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 454</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my i. and truth to you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.172" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 172</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>